Hindi ka ba naabala niyan ngayon?

01:35:10.579 --> 01:35:11.497
Ah.

01:35:12.123 --> 01:35:13.499
Hindi, hindi talaga.

01:35:14.250 --> 01:35:16.293
Matagal na kaming tapos ni Liana.

01:35:17.920 --> 01:35:19.463
Hindi ka pa rin naka-move on.

01:35:24.427 --> 01:35:26.929
-[pagbuhos ng likido]
-Hindi ko matiis ang ganyang bagay.

01:35:29.265 --> 01:35:30.599
Nalinlang.

01:35:33.102 --> 01:35:34.437
Pinagtaksilan.

01:35:38.607 --> 01:35:40.067
Hindi ko mapapatawad 'yan.

