Hindi totoo iyan.

01:39:29.713 --> 01:39:31.715
[madamdaming musikang tumutugtog gamit ang piano]

01:39:53.195 --> 01:39:54.446
Sa huli…

01:40:03.122 --> 01:40:05.249
